OL,3,CPower NI to increase household
OL,4,Celectricity prices by 4%
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland's biggest energy
OL,7,Fsupplier, Power NI, is to increase
OL,8,Fhousehold electricity bills by 4%.
OL,10,FThe move, affecting more than 500,000
OL,11,Fhomes, will come into effect at the
OL,12,Fstart of December.
OL,14,FThe price rise, which is the first in
OL,15,Ftwo years, comes after four successive
OL,16,Fcuts in the tariff.
OL,18,FA typical customer will see their
OL,19,Fbills increase by about #38 per year.
