OL,3,CPower NI to increase household
OL,4,Celectricity prices by 4%
OL,6,FPower NI said the decision reflected
OL,7,Fincreases in market operation and
OL,8,Fnetwork-related charges.
OL,10,FThe tariff change has been approved by
OL,11,Fthe Utility Regulator and applies to
OL,12,Fdomestic customers only.
OL,14,FPower NI is the only price-controlled
OL,15,Felectricity supplier in Northern
OL,16,FIreland.
OL,18,FWilliam Steele, director of Power NI
OL,19,FCustomer Solutions, said: "We work
OL,20,Fhard to keep our prices as low as
OL,21,Fpossible.
