OL,3,CPower NI to increase household
OL,4,Celectricity prices by 4%
OL,6,F"However, wholesale prices remain high
OL,7,Fand significant increases in third
OL,8,Fparty market operation and network-
OL,9,Frelated costs have regrettably
OL,10,Fnecessitated a tariff increase.
OL,12,F"In these challenging times, we have
OL,13,Fheld off changing prices for as long
OL,14,Fas possible and we have been able to
OL,15,Fkeep our tariffs below the equivalent
OL,16,FGB and RoI average."
OL,18,FA review by the Utility Regulator
OL,19,Fdetermined that a 4% increase was
OL,20,Fneeded.
