OL,3,CPower NI to increase household
OL,4,Celectricity prices by 4%
OL,6,FLeigh Greer, head of security of
OL,7,Fsupply and markets regulation at the
OL,8,FUtility Regulator, said: "The main
OL,9,Freason for this tariff change is due
OL,10,Fto an increase in costs related to the
OL,11,Fmarket and operation of the
OL,12,Felectricity network.
OL,14,F"As we continue to strive to meet
OL,15,FGovernment climate change targets, and
OL,16,Fto ensure security of supply, there
OL,17,Fhas been a need to invest in grid
OL,18,Finfrastructure to facilitate renewable
OL,19,Fenergy sources.
