OL,3,CPower NI to increase household
OL,4,Celectricity prices by 4%
OL,6,F"In addition, we have seen significant
OL,7,Fincreases in wholesale gas costs
OL,8,Fglobally as a result of the ongoing
OL,9,Fconflicts in the Middle East.
OL,10,FWholesale gas prices affect the cost
OL,11,Fof electricity because 45% of
OL,12,Felectricity is generated with gas-
OL,13,Ffired power stations.
OL,15,F"The average price of regulated
OL,16,Felectricity for households in Northern
OL,17,FIreland is around #80 cheaper per year
OL,18,Fthan in Great Britain, and around #180
OL,19,Fcheaper than in Ireland."
